div.p: sql SELECT COUNT(*) FROM clicks WHERE short_code = $1
sql SELECT COUNT(*) FROM clicks WHERE short_code = $1 AND clicked_at >= $2
sql SELECT referer, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM clicks WHERE short_code = $1 AND referer IS NOT NULL GROUP BY referer ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 5
sql SELECT date_trunc('day', clicked_at AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') AS period, COUNT(*) AS clicks FROM clicks WHERE short_code = $1 GROUP BY period ORDER BY period ASC
